{"tid":1771713,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有人叫前線入港島都有300正皮？","createTime":"2019-12-06T05:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T07:16:51.000Z","uid":57221,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d272e8f578fce0348df49c38809154ce92a61625","tid":1771713,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"原post：<br />\n<br />\n前線手足建議呢個兩日盡量做好planning， 由於港島地勢非常差，務必要做好事前計劃: safe house (如可行) ，逃生路線，換裝地點 (特別係女手足)<br />\n如果可行就出去踩下線，準備定逃生門<br />\n唔係做休息撚，只係前線小一個就小一個，一定要盡所有能力保住前線<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nwtf？<br />\n前線咪撚去港島啊<br />\n痴撚線<br />\n前線去港島簡直係預約拘捕<br />\n想做前線絕對唔好入港島<br />\n任由和理非被捕就ok<br />\n<br />\n48小時同10年嘅分別<br />\n再重申一次<br />\n勇武唔好入港島<br />\n和理非絕對唔需要勇武保護<br />\n需要保護嘅係勇武而唔係和理非<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住係民陣吹雞就一定過百萬人 你唔做好宣傳一樣係得四五十萬人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1771606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1771606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f416f0bd7b02c3af1583b1446a2f36606bd3c90a","tid":1771713,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到所有人見到<br />\n唔好比嗰個post spin到<br />\n前線係唔需要入港島<br />\n入港島代表你啀化身為和理非<br />\n並非前線</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9478f9dd033b0bde871002ca800d20054080d904","tid":1771713,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成個post竟然冇人屌呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係大開眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ccded62df5b555a793024875048b5a9709cd834f","tid":1771713,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:17:12.000Z","msg":"原樓主道歉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"5030f4d90777129